function.json_organizer:
begin
obligation( Acknowledge INGV, [ ], action = "publish" ).
attribute( INGV, string "Instituto Nazionale Di Geofisica E Vulcanologia" ).
obligation( Include CC_BY_SA_4 , [ ], action = "publish" ).
attribute( CC_BY_SA_4, url "https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by/4.0/" ).
end
function.PE_stationxml_reader:
begin
obligation( Cite AC_network , [ ], stage = "import" ).
attribute( AC_network, string "Institute Of Geosciences, Energy, Water And Environment. (2002). Albanian Seismological Network [Data set]. International Federation of Digital Seismograph Networks. https://doi.org/10.7914/SN/AC" ).

obligation( Acknowledge ORFEUS_EIDA , [ ], action = "publish" ).
attribute( ORFEUS_EIDA, string "We acknowledge ORFEUS and EIDA for providing the waveform data." ).
end
